codex
The skeletal code confirms one important asymmetry: it builds render commands with a D3D9-style vertex window from the IB’s min/max, but the IB values themselves are copied unchanged. Next I’m following those arguments through Graphics and the two backends to see exactly where D3D11 loses the range.
