codex
There is a more concrete source than a vague LOD mismatch: `MeshConstructionHelper` stores `m_shaderVertexIndex` on global `VertexData`, while per-shader data holds lists of those global vertex data indices. I’m checking whether the builder has per-shader remap state or whether one shader can overwrite another shader’s compact index.
