- **`Direct3d11_Device.cpp` `present()` ~@868: serialization diagnostic ENABLED** (`#if 1`). It creates one static `ID3D11Query` (EVENT) and after `Present` does `Flush()` + `End(query)` + spin on `GetData` until the GPU finishes the frame Ã¢â€ â€™ forces full CPUÃ¢â€ â€GPU serialization (kills pipelining; static query avoids per-frame CreateQuery/Release churn). This is the ONLY functional change vs baseline.
