>    splitting legacy `sampler2D`. specmap_bump samples `normalMap` before `diffuseMap` Ã¢â€ â€™ normalMap=t0,
>    diffuseMap=t1, opposite the engine's D3D9 stage-index SRV bind Ã¢â€ â€™ the blue normal map was sampled as
>    albedo. Fixed by a reflection-driven stageÃ¢â€ â€™SRV-slot remap (`Direct3d11_PixelShaderProgramData::
>    getSrvSlotForStage`, used in `Direct3d11_StaticShaderData::apply`). Also added the VS material c11Ã¢â‚¬â€œc15
