1496-	// -TRF- come back to this, implement as sorted vectors.  duplicates are fine at add time.  do sort and unique at prepareForReading() time.

codex
The important code-level split is now clear. Tri lists are remapped through `m_shaderVertexIndex`; tri strips are not. For the reported `drawPartialIndexedTriangleList` path, an out-of-range max means the remap invariant has already failed or stale/corrupt indices were built into the static IB, rather than D3D11 inventing bad indices.
